S.FORM: I 1968 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 29 a romi'ad masofoc ci Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Croatia anini i ci Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović, patirengan a romi'ad i 2015 a miheca saka 2 folad saka 19 a romi'ad. Her presidential term ended on 18 February 2020.
